data.description: Well-maintained home nestled on just under a half acre and located just minutes from shopping, dining, & entertainment. This home is only 20 miles from Downtown Weatherford & less than 5 miles from Granbury's Historic Downtown Square. Open concept living area with high ceilings and corner fireplace. The floor plan flows together to create and warm and inviting atmosphere whether it be for football parties this fall or holiday gatherings come winter. Big windows allow for tons of natural light and neutral tones throughout mean this home is ready for your style. Island kitchen features granite counters, tones of cabinet space, huge farm sink, and stainless steel appliances that all tie together for crisp and clean look. Do not miss the master bathroom! This en-suite boasts a massive walk-in shower with 2 shower heads with separate controls. The backyard is terraced with a stone retaining wall & fence that lead to the rest of the yard & trees. This one is waiting for you to call it home!
